{
  "id": "threshold-construct",
  "purpose": "Threshold direct construction: all five quantifiers accepted; number/total and percent/available combinations accepted; unknown quantifier and unknown quantifier_type members raise ValueError('Invalid quantifier'/'Invalid quantifier type'); a bare-string quantifier_type fails the membership check on its characters (same 'Invalid quantifier type'); a length-1 quantifier_type raises IndexError at [1]; and thresh is stored with NO validation \u2014 negative and non-numeric values pass and to_tuple() returns them verbatim.",
  "runtime_class": "smoke",
  "provenance": "docs/surface.md type:Threshold all input classes except interacts-forall; threshold.py:14-41 at the pin; screened live 2026-07-07 (screen_types.py)",
